name: .VSMETA File Extension
summary: Learn about .VSMETA files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: VSMETA files are not meant to be opened. If you want to edit the metadata a VSMETA file contains, locate the associated video in Synology Video Station (Web) and edit the video's metadata there.
